&lt;p style=&quot;margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px&quot;&gt;If things seem hopelessly broken and you want a completely fresh configuration, check the 'Are you sure?' checkbox and click 'START OVER'. These actions will completely remove the existing configuration and exit the program. The WhatsNowPlaying directory in Documents will stay, however.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
